  ],
  "remarks": "JSC Novo-Vyatka is a manufacturer of weapons and ammunition and therefore part of the Russian military-industrial complex. In 2023 and 2024, JSC Novo-Vyatka received state subsidies under a programme designed to finance training of military industry workers of selected entities. JSC Novo-Vyatka therefore materially supports and benefits from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
